title.narrative: RY TAIZ MUNICIPAL DEV & FLOOD PROTEC

description.narrative: The Objectives of the Project are to assist the Recipient in: (a) protecting residents, economic activities and infrastructure from destructive effects of seasonal flooding in Taiz, Hadramout and AlMahra; (b) restoring access to critical road infrastructure damaged by the floods; and (c) strenhgthening the capacity of local governments and support decentralization.
